#--------------------------------------------------#
#			       EXTERNAL LIBRARIES              #
#--------------------------------------------------#
The platform needs external libraries installed on the computer to work :

_ Lapack : version 3.0
	Lapack++, delivered with the platform, must be recompiled. You have to indicate the path
	to your Lapack library in ext/Lapack++/Makefile.def, and compile with the command :
	make libs "CPP=g++ -Wno-deprecated".

_ ODEPACK

_ libf2c

_ libxml : version 2-2.6.9.
	Be careful to edit siconos.csh and give the path to your libxml in the environment variable LD_LIBRARY_PATH.
	
For these 4 libraries, you have to precise their path in the file Makefile.inc of the platform.


#--------------------------------------------------#
#			COMPILATION OF THE PLUGINS             #
#--------------------------------------------------# 
g++ -g -fbounds-check -w -Wno-deprecated -fPIC -c <plugin>.c -o <plugin>.o
g++ -g -fbounds-check -w -Wno-deprecated -fPIC -shared -W -O -o <plugin>.so <plugin>.o
